s sociales Facebook, en Overseas Press Club of Puerto Rico y en Twitter, en @opcpr. Moderadores: Héctor Pérez Cintrón, presidente del OPC; Ángel Bosch de León, secretario del OPC y Milly Méndez, periodista y asesora de medios.\r\n\r\n(Para mas información: <a href=\"http://opcpr.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.opcpr.com</a> - <a href=\"mailto:opcpr@yahoo.com\" target=\"_blank\">opcpr@yahoo.com</a> 787-408-3033 o 787-354-4029)','Julián Herencia conversa con el Overseas Press Club de Puerto Rico','','inherit','open','open','','797-revision-v1','','','2013-11-05 03:49:04','2013-11-05 03:49:04','',797,'http://thejsj.com/2013/opcpr/?p=983',0,'revision','',0),(986,1,'2013-11-05 04:23:04','2013-11-05 04:23:04','Sample description. Sample description. Sample description. Sample description. Sample description.','Lo que es Noticia: Noviembre, 4, 2010','','publish','closed','closed','','lo-que-es-noticia-noviembre-4-2010','','','2013-11-05 04:23:51','2013-11-05 04:23:51','',0,'http://thejsj.com/2013/opcpr/?post_type=opc_radio_show&#038;p=986',0,'opc_radio_show','',0),(987,1,'2013-11-05 04:20:52','2013-11-05 04:20:52','','Overseas-Press-Club-Puerto-Rico-Logo-200','','inherit','open','open','','overseas-press-club-puerto-rico-logo-200-2','','','2013-11-05 04:20:52','2013-11-05 04:20:52','',986,'http://thejsj.com/2013/opcpr/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/Overseas-Press-Club-Puerto-Rico-Logo-200.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(988,1,'2013-11-05 04:21:05','2013-11-05 04:21:05','','OPCpromoJULIAN-HERENCIA2','','inherit','open','open','','opcpromojulian-herencia2-2','','','2013-11-05 04:21:05','2013-11-05 04:21:05','',986,'http://thejsj.com/2013/opcpr/wp-content/uploads/2013/11/OPCpromoJULIAN-HERENCIA2.pdf',0,'attachment','application/pdf',0),(989,1,'2013-11-05 04:22:36','2013-11-05 04:22:36','\"Mozart - Symphony No. 40, III\" from Fall 2001 Concert by Columbia University Orchestra. Released: 2002.','Mozart - Symphony No. 40, III','','inherit','open','open','','mozart-symphony-no-40-iii